data.description: Nifty Victorian circa 1890 complete with Turret located in Schnecksville right next to where the new Medical Center, Wawa and stores will be located. Excellent location for Professional Office, Residence or both. 4 Bedrooms in the Main house and 2 full baths. Separate Carriage House with great potential for additional living space.  Large Lot with plenty of parking.
